description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to join the administration team within the Crisis Response Service (based at Eastbourne DGH and Conquest Hospital).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for experienced administrators to deliver the role of Coordination Support Administrator on Saturdays and Sundays, on a 6 Month Fixed Term Contract.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role currently provides invaluable support to the shift coordinator and community staff during core working hours, ensuring smooth service delivery. The role requires excellent organisational and ICT skills, as well as the ability to remain calm, professional and methodical in a busy office environment. The successful candidate will have substantial administration experience and enjoy working as part of a fast-paced multi-disciplinary team. If you have experience supporting a busy team and enjoy the challenge of working in a developing service, then we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameMagda BarkerJob titleService ManagerEmail addressmagda.barker@nhs.netTelephone number07974 191301&lt;/p&gt;
